    Interface IModel

    A model is a composite object which may contain a map of paths, or a map of models recursively.

    interface IModel {
        caption?: ICaption;
        exporterOptions?: { [exporterName: string]: any };
        layer?: string;
        models?: IModelMap;
        notes?: string;
        origin?: IPoint;
        paths?: IPathMap;
        type?: string;
        units?: string;
    }
